posting_body: ['Sierra Ridge Apartments - A place to call home!', 'You can now apply online at <URL>', 'Bed: 2 / Bath: 1 Unfurnished  Apt', 'Sq.', 'Footage: 850 ft', 'Rent: $1595.00/month', 'Sierra Ridge Apartment Homes is located in Tehachapi, just minutes away from amazing restaurants and A brand new Wal-Mart supercenter that is NOW OPEN!', ' Sierra Ridge offers the comforts of home while offering the convenience of urban living and provide many amenities that suit your active lifestyle.', ' Our on-site management team is committed to responsive service and meticulous maintenance assuring that you can always come home to the very best.', "Call or come by today and you'll discover Sierra Ridge Apartments is the perfect home for you.", 'Our apartment homes feature:', '-- Central Air & Heating', '--- Refrigerator', '----Gas Stove', '---Microwave', '---TV', '-- Dishwasher', '-- Patio or Balcony', '---Basic Cable', 'Our Residents enjoy:', '---Sparkling Pool', '-- Covered Parking', '-- Large trees and lawn areas', '-- Furnished Available', 'Dogs and Cats welcome.', '$500.00 security deposit OAC.', 'Under 20lbs at adult age.', 'No full Breeds', 'Please.', 'Breed Restriction.', 'Weight Restriction.']
